  <section id="system" class="voiceminer-page__system">
   <div class="voiceminer-page__system-heading heading-container">
     <h2 class="heading-number heading-number--04 ">
  <span class="heading-number__title">システム構成</span>
</h2>
     <p class="heading-description">
      音声認識システムと連携をする場合、リアルタイム型とバッチ型ではフローが異なります。リアルタイム型はPBXから音声データを取得して音声認識システムでテキスト化を行い、テキスト情報をリアルタイムにVextRecommend、VextResumeに受け渡します。また、VextResumeで要約した結果は応対履歴としてCRMに連携します。バッチ型は通話録音装置から音声データを取得して音声認識システムでテキスト化を行い、蓄積データをVextMinerに受け渡して分析処理を行い、結果をVextPortalに反映して情報共有を行います。
     </p>
   </div>
   <div class="voiceminer-page__system-flow js-scroll-show">
    <div class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-container voiceminer-page__system-flow-container--realtime">
      <div class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-detail voiceminer-page__system-flow-detail--realtime">
        <h3 class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-realtime-heading heading-point">リアルタイム型</h3>
        <img class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-realtime-image u-hidden-pc" src="https://www.vext.co.jp/wp-content/themes/vext-corp-2019/assets/images/voiceminer-flow-realtime-sp.png" alt="Real time system flow">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-detail voiceminer-page__system-flow-container--source">
      <div class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-all-container">
        <img class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-all-image u-hidden-sp" src="https://www.vext.co.jp/wp-content/themes/vext-corp-2019/assets/images/voiceminer-flow_all.png" alt="System flow">
      </div>
      <img class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-source-image u-hidden-pc" src="https://www.vext.co.jp/wp-content/themes/vext-corp-2019/assets/images/voiceminer-flow-source-sp.png" alt="Source system flow">
    </div>
    <div class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-container voiceminer-page__system-flow-container--batch">
      <div class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-detail voiceminer-page__system-flow-detail--batch">
        <h3 class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-batch-heading heading-point u-hidden-pc">バッチ型</h3>
        <img class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-batch-image u-hidden-pc" src="https://www.vext.co.jp/wp-content/themes/vext-corp-2019/assets/images/voiceminer-flow-batch-sp.png" alt="Batch type system flow">
        <h3 class="voiceminer-page__system-flow-batch-heading heading-point u-hidden-sp">バッチ型</h3>
      </div>
  </div>
   </div>
  </section>
